<p class="noPspace header"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">Awaited Ticket Return or Support</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">If you can&rsquo;t use your tickets, please return them so others can attend the show. You don&rsquo;t have to return all of your tickets, just the ones you don&rsquo;t need. To return your tickets, please call the support number at <strong>513.731.7400 ext 1589&nbsp;</strong>or email the following to&nbsp;<strong>awaitedsupport@crossroads.net</strong>. If you are leaving a voicemail, please include a phone number in the event that we need to call you back. Thank you.&nbsp;</span></p>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div><span style="color: #292929; font-family: &rsquo;Helvetica Neue&rsquo;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">1. First &amp; Last Name on the reservation</span></div>
<div><span style="color: #292929; font-family: &rsquo;Helvetica Neue&rsquo;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">2. The event (date &amp; time) the ticket is for</span></div>
<div><span style="color: #292929; font-family: &rsquo;Helvetica Neue&rsquo;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">3. The barcode (# on the right of your ticket) OR email address used to reserve the tickets</span></div>
<div><span style="color: #292929; font-family: &rsquo;Helvetica Neue&rsquo;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">4. Section, row &amp; seat numbers you are returning</span></div>
<div><span style="color: #292929; font-family: &rsquo;Helvetica Neue&rsquo;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></div>
<div><span style="color: #292929; font-family: &rsquo;Helvetica Neue&rsquo;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Note&ndash;if you are reserving handicap tickets, please call the number above or email <strong>awaitedsupport@crossroads.net</strong>. Please include information regarding your preferred show date &amp; time and how many handicap seats are required.&nbsp;</span></div>
